became a skeleton through magic.

【Skeleton Head】 There are occasionally people
whose bodies undergo changes due to accidents
during magical experiments, but I'm not that kind
of magician.
【Skeleton Head】 It's simply a hobby.
【Skeleton Head】 Isn't it cool?

know.

to sleep.

head, right?

a part of my body.

started wanting to see your true face.

【Masamune】 Why not? It's just a little bit.
